entry.title: aritram1/Superbadge-Data-Integration-Specialist
entry.summary: 'Data Integration Specialist' is one of the superbadges of Salesforce trailhead(A New Approach to Learning Salesforce). This superbadge is specially designed for learning and testing integrations between different systems. This repository is for solving all the problems in the way of earning the superbadge.
